import React, { useCallback } from 'react' import { Layout, Typography, Row, Col } from 'antd' import styled from 'styled-components' import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' import { useDispatch, useSelector } from 'react-redux' import { logoutAction } from '../../reducers' const { Header } = Layout const { Title } = Typography function Navbar() { const navigate = useNavigate() const isLoggedIn = useSelector((state) => state.user.isLoggedIn) const dispatch = useDispatch() const onLogOut = useCallback(() => { dispatch(logoutAction()) }, []) return (
navigate('/')}> 지금 나의 하루는
글 작성 글 검색 글 보기
{!isLoggedIn ? (
로그인 회원가입
) : (
마이페이지 로그아웃
)}
) } const StyledTitle = styled(Title)` text-align: center; margin: 1.2rem 1rem 1rem 1rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); ` const StyledLink = styled(Link)` color: #38532e; padding: 0 1rem; ` export default Navbar
